    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/bac764f3d560f38400789a12b5fd244c.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><br>丹玛加列亚王国的公主—艾莉亚，为了王位的继承仪式而来到了边境的小村庄—拉帝贝勒。 然而艾莉亚公主却在拉帝贝勒被卷入了与神秘组织—「教团」之间的战斗。 伴随着战斗的结束，艾莉亚公主也发现了令人震惊的真相……。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/c4bb294d41b529d4a18b8f15af469896.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ARIA CHRONICLE的特征</h2></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个性丰富的角色们</h2>在本作当中，除了拥有清纯可爱的外貌与不屈不饶意志的公主—艾莉亚之外， 还有着许多不同个性的角色会陆续登场。<br>不仅是身旁的伙伴，就连在迷宫中遇到的敌人也同样经过精心的设计。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/1a45b349bb716854251722e347a630cb.poster.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/1a45b349bb716854251722e347a630cb.webm?t=1678440232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/1a45b349bb716854251722e347a630cb.mp4?t=1678440232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・富有战略性的回合制战斗</h2>在战斗当中，每一回合都有着截然不同的变化，使战斗变得更有战略性、更有趣。此外，随着每一位角色「心智值」的变化，战斗的过程也会受到大幅度的影响。因此要如何发挥队伍的最大效率，以及即时分析战况都是玩家特别需要注重的地方。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/e5d55dfbbb4a2023fef50a716f1df263.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・自由客制化的游戏系统</h2>队伍中最多可以配置五名角色进行冒险。而主角艾莉亚有着多达14种的职业可供选择，同行的伙伴们也会有各自的装备、技能、特质等等的要素可供选择，玩家可以依据自己的喜好组成属于自己的专属队伍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/dbf5dc1d6601afe57564118d88ef8280.poster.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/dbf5dc1d6601afe57564118d88ef8280.webm?t=1678440232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/3ba994cd13370055670de166c0e3d3fb.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/60616f8d55582a41a8a07b4b8ef1d854.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・具有挑战性的任务</h2>游戏中的迷宫都是随机生成的，因此每次重新进入关卡时都会是全新的冒险体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/5205c61d016ac40da882eaedc8553863.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><br><br>队伍中的伙伴会因为关卡中的负面行动而造成能力值下降，甚至有脱离队伍的情况，因此在进行冒险的同时，思考如何发挥伙伴们的战斗力也是非常重要的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1229900/extras/f6241492a0407928fcf4a5bc05adc712.avif?t=1678440232\" width=600 height=330 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >・富有深度的剧情</h2>在边境的小村庄—拉帝贝勒的冒险会随着故事的进展渐渐变的壮阔。 <br>或许会有与想像中完全不同的发展也说不定，请玩家尽情享受故事吧。",
